What is BG5™?
BG5™ is the Career &amp; Business Application of the Human Design System.
We look specially at the most basic and fundamental issue that all human beings have to face&hellip;
How to be successful materially in our job, career or business.
Meaning, according to our design&hellip;
 How are we designed to make money? How can we fulfill our purpose? What gifts get “called out” of us in large or small groups?
